HEADWORD: Replum
<hw>Re"plum</hw> <pr>(r?"pl?m)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
doorcase.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The framework of some pods, as
the cress, which remains after the valves drop off.</def>
